ve in a variety of charitable and forprofit ventures through a wholly owned entity balance vector inc his charity initiatives are primarily focused on global environmental issues and programs to help atrisk children in the urban centers of the united states and the rural areas of sicily and he is a major donor to stanford university and hospital the world wildlife fund and the palo alto medical foundation in  to recognize his support for education in service to the italian republic italys president sergio mattarella honored luczo with the title cavaliere dell’ordine della stella d’italia a knighthood known in english as the order of the star of italian solidarity he has served on the boards of directors of microsoft corporation including serving on the ceo search committee and as chairman of the compensation committee veritas software and vmware luczo also served on the advisory boards of the new york stock exchange nyse and the stanford graduate school of business in  institutional investor magazine ranked luczo among the worlds top  ceos of it hardware  electronics manufacturing services companies based on the votes of sellside analysts in  the magazine ranked him a top  ceo in the same category based on buyside analysts votes and in  he was ranked a top  ceo by sellside analysts in the same category in  harvard business review ranked luczo number  among the bestperforming ceos in the world in  cnn money named luczo among the  top performing ceos in america and harvard business review ranked luczo number  among the top  bestperforming ceos in the world in  bloomberg ranked luczo no  among its top  list of technology leaders in august  luczo was awarded the darjah setia pangkuan negeri dspn the order of the defender of state — knight commander mylaysia which carries the title of dato for his contributions to the state of penang in  luczo was ranked st on fortune magazines top  businesspersons of the year contents  early life  early career  seagate  return  balance 